I'm not too sure on a lot of these chords, so feel free to let me know if you think any of them should be different. Also, sorry for the excessive power chords in the chorus, I tried using less chords but it didn't sound right, so I just decided to write out each power chord. The Cmaj7b5 is interchangeable with Cmaj7, so you play whatever sounds better to you (or whatever's easier for you). Enjoy :).
